                "invention-title": [
                    "Offshore wind turbine coupling energy storage double-floating system",
                    "海上风力机耦合储能双浮动系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses an offshore wind turbine coupling energy storage double-floating system which comprises a tension leg platform and a wind turbine, and the wind turbine is installed on a floating body base of the tension leg platform. A hydrogen energy storage device is arranged on the tension leg platform and can convert electric energy and hydrogen energy so as to store and store wind power generated by the wind turbine. The hydrogen energy storage device is a suspended body, and the suspended hydrogen energy storage device is flexibly connected with the floating body base; the wind turbine is in limiting fit with the hydrogen energy storage device, the wind turbine generates horizontal constraint on the hydrogen energy storage device, and flexible connection between the floating body base and the hydrogen energy storage device generates vertical constraint on the hydrogen energy storage device; the wind turbine is provided with a vertical tower, and a limiting hole is formed in the hydrogen energy storage device; the tower is correspondingly located in the limiting hole so as to horizontally restrain the hydrogen energy storage device. And the floating body base is connected with the hydrogen energy storage device through a rope body so as to generate vertical constraint on the hydrogen energy storage device. The method can effectively solve the problem of wind abandoning and electricity limiting of offshore wind power in the deep sea area, and the wind energy utilization rate is increased."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了海上风力机耦合储能双浮动系统，包括张力腿平台和风力机，风力机安装于张力腿平台的浮体基座上；张力腿平台上设置有氢储能装置，氢储能装置能将电能与氢能进行转化，以储放风力机产生的风电；氢储能装置为悬浮体，悬浮的氢储能装置与浮体基座柔性连接；风力机与氢储能装置限位配合，风力机对氢储能装置产生水平约束，浮体基座与氢储能装置的柔性连接对氢储能装置产生垂向约束；风力机具有竖向的塔架，氢储能装置上形成有限位孔；塔架对应位于限位孔内，以对氢储能装置产生水平约束；浮体基座通过绳体连接氢储能装置，以对氢储能装置产生垂向约束。本发明能够有效解决深海区域海上风电的弃风限电问题，提高风能利用率。"
                }
